3a9a5a54-23f6-49ae-a3f5-5b79070d9419.do_description: To make the output, you have to...keep the light blue cube in the same exact location. Then copy and move the other shape directly towards the blue cube, until it is touching it. At the end you'll have the light blue cube in the same exact spot as in the input grid and the the other shape will be the same but moved directly towards and touching the blue cube.
3a9a5a54-23f6-49ae-a3f5-5b79070d9419.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input grid.
3a9a5a54-23f6-49ae-a3f5-5b79070d9419.see_description: In the input, you should see...a light blue cube and a red shape.
